WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:03.700
I'm going to see my dad

2
00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:06.400
I haven't seen him since my parents got divorced

3
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:08.700
Because he hurt our mother too deeply back then

4
00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:10.420
Our mother almost jumped off the building back then

5
00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:12.100
So I swear

6
00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:13.660
Never see you again

7
00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:15.300
Then why did you go again?

8
00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:16.520
Because of you.

9
00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.300
