15
00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:31.020
That's why I've been looking for me

16
00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:34.040
But I can't lose my opportunity for that money

17
00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:36.440
But then I gave in because of you

18
00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:37.620
What because of me

19
00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:39.220
You say your personality

20
00:00:39.480 --> 00:00:42.260
Maybe one day the lawyer's license will be revoked

21
00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:46.140
How can I support you if I don't have any money in my hand?

22
00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:47.820
So I bowed to my dad

23
00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:49.840
Who let him have money in his hands?

24
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.800
In case something happens to you

25
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:53.540
I can still fish you out with money

26
00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:56.280
Humph

27
00:00:56.920 --> 00:01:02.580
Get up, get up, get up, oh, husband, does it hurt? I'll rub it for you. Don't you blame me for not having integrity?

28
